title: Ep. - 391 - 9/11 FIRST RESPONDER: PENTAGON RETIRED GREEN BERET JOSEPH HEALEY
description:
Kate discusses several documentaries about the September 11, 2001 attacks including Apple TV’s new documentary 9/11: Inside the President’s War Room, featuring interviews with President George W. Bush and his chief of staff and closest advisors at the time of 9/11.  

Retired Army Ranger and Green Beret Joe Healey discusses being a first responder at The Pentagon on September 11, 2001, and the mental health toll of first responders and veterans.  

Reality Life with Kate Casey
